bio: Tom is our top-performing negotiator with a passion for helping families find their perfect home. Specializes in the M20/M21 areas.
Sarah leads our Didsbury branch with over 12 years of industry experience. Known for exceptional client service and team development.
James specializes in helping first-time buyers navigate the property market. Patient and thorough approach to client care.
Emma is our lead valuer with exceptional local market knowledge. Achieved 92% instruction rate from valuations in 2023.
Michael manages our sales through to completion with a 94% success rate. Expert at chain management and problem-solving.
Lisa focuses on apartment sales and buy-to-let investments. Strong relationships with local landlords and investors.
David joined us as a trainee valuer and has quickly developed excellent property assessment skills.
Rachel keeps our office running smoothly, handling compliance documentation and client communications.
Chris manages our property marketing, photography coordination, and social media presence.
Sophie heads our lettings department with expertise in tenant relations and property management.
Daniel specializes in period properties and character homes in the Chorlton area.
Victoria manages our Chorlton branch and is known for her strategic approach to property sales.
Ryan is our new build specialist with strong developer relationships across Greater Manchester.
Hannah ensures smooth transactions from offer acceptance to completion with excellent communication skills.
Oliver is our newest team member, eager to learn and develop his career in estate agency.
Charlotte provides accurate valuations across the Chorlton and Stretford areas.
Jack handles weekend viewings and provides vital support during our busiest periods.
Amy oversees all compliance matters including AML checks and regulatory requirements.
Mark maintains our CRM systems and provides technical support across all branches.
Jennifer manages all financial operations including commission processing and vendor invoicing.
